  "Name": {
    "English": "LOST ANGLER'S RIG",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "迷途垂钓者的渔具",
    "TraditionalChinese": "失落垂釣者的裝備"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Lost Angler's Rig",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "迷途垂钓者的渔具",
    "TraditionalChinese": "失落垂釣者的裝備"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Unique Angling Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "独特垂钓装置",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的垂釣裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A versatile piece of <span class=\"name name-technology\">angling equipment</span>, enabling the user to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fish</span> in a variety of water conditions. This rig was once owned by the legendary <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Lost Angler</span>.<br><br>Access the fishing rig by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> and cast your line into a body of water with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>. With a fish hooked, press and hold <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> to haul in your catch.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "多功能<span class=\"name name-technology\">垂钓装备</span>，允许使用者在各类水体环境中进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">垂钓</span>。曾经属于传说中的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">迷途垂钓者</span>的渔具。<br><br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>启用渔具并使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>抛竿。鱼上钩时长按<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>收线并收取你的渔获。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一套萬用的<span class=\"name name-technology\">垂釣裝備</span>，能協助使用者在各種水域條件下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">釣魚</span>。這套釣具曾經是傳奇人物<span class=\"name name-stellar\">失落垂釣者</span>的所有物。<br><br>若要使用這套釣具，請按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>，然後使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 將魚線拋入水中。待魚上鉤後，按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 即可將魚釣上來。"
  },
